data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch-style home nestled in the community of Parma. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms, this residence offers a comfortable and inviting living space. As you enter, you'll be greeted by the timeless elegance of hardwood floors, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The spacious living room is perfect for relaxing or entertaining, while the adjacent dining area provides a cozy space for family meals. Plus, with the added convenience of new central air installed in 2022, you'll stay cool and comfortable year-round. Outside, the property offers a detached 2-car garage, providing plenty of space for parking and storage. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this wonderful property your own!
